{"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10-136-Calendar-Integration-with-Event-Kit","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The Event Kit and Event Kit UI frameworks together allow iPhone OS applications to access event information from a user’s Calendar database. You can fetch events based on a date range or a unique identifier, receive notifications when event records change, and allow users to create and edit events for any of their local and server-based calendars. Learn techniques to take advantage of these features and other useful tips from Apple engineers."}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/wwdc10-136-calendar-integration-with-event-kit"]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sampleCodeDownload":{"kind":"sampleDownload","action":{"type":"reference","overridingTitle":"Open on WWDCIndex","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/nonstrict.eu\/wwdcindex\/wwdc2010\/136\/"}},"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"😱 “No Overview Available!”","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Be the hero to change that by watching the video or reading the transcript on WWDCIndex and providing notes! It’s super easy:"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/wwdcnotes.com\/documentation\/wwdcnotes\/contributing"}]}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes","doc:\/\/WWDCNotes\/documentation\/WWDCNotes\/WWDC10"]]},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"WWDC Notes"}],"roleHeading":"WWDC10","role":"sampleCode","title":"Calendar Integration with Event Kit"},"references":{"WWDCNotes.png":{"type":"image","variants":[{"url":"\/images\/WWDCNotes\/WWDCNotes.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"alt":null,"i